9"></span>这个时候要有应对的智慧，<span class="_ _9"></span>无论如何要</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 ya6 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">坚持下去。 </div><div class="t m0 x1b h4 ya7 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">人生在世，<span class="_ _7"></span>应当尽量行持善法。<span class="_ _7"></span>在这方面，<span class="_ _7"></span>我们需要有</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 ya8 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">所规划，<span class="_ _7"></span>比如一年做几次善法，<span class="_ _7"></span>或者一个月做几次善法。<span class="_ _7"></span>否</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 ya9 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">则，<span class="_ _7"></span>每天浑浑噩噩地度日，<span class="_ _7"></span>除了为生计奔波，<span class="_ _7"></span>什么有意义的</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yce ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">事情都不做，<span class="_ _7"></span>那当你离开人间时，<span class="_ _7"></span>回顾自己一生，<span class="_ _7"></span>恐怕会有</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yd9 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">很多遗憾。 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
